ah</i> ‘stranger’, or <i>gisil</i> ‘pledge’. Medieval forms can be found to support all these theories, and it is possible that several names have fallen together, or that the name was subjected to reanalysis by folk etymology at an early date."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Geoffrey De Horderne was born about 1176, in Durham, England, United Kingdom, his father, R26 Richard HORDERNE, was 26 and his mother, ?, was 23. He had at least 1 son with ?."},"et":{"ABT 1176–":"umbes 1176–Surnud","1176–Male":"1176–Surnud","1179–Female":"1179–Surnud","–Male":"Surnud","1152–Male":"1152–Surnud","1155–Female":"1155–Surnud","ABT 1176":"umbes 1176","1179":"1179","1155":"1155","1176":"1176","1152":"1152","HORDENE, DURHAM, ENGLAND":"Durham, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"ABT 1176–":"noin 1176–Kuollut","1176–Male":"1176–Kuollut","1179–Female":"1179–Kuollut","–Male":"Kuollut","1152–Male":"1152–Kuollut","1155–Female":"1155–Kuollut","ABT 1176":"noin 1176","1179":"1179","1155":"1155","1176":"1176","1152":"1152","HORDENE, DURHAM, ENGLAND":"Durham, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"ABT 1176–":"environ 1176–Décédé","1176–Male":"1176–Décédé","1179–Female":"1179–Décédée","–Male":"Décédé","1152–Male":"1152–Décédé","1155–Female":"1155–Décédée","ABT 1176":"environ 1176","1179":"1179","1155":"1155","1176":"1176","1152":"1152","HORDENE, DURHAM, ENGLAND":"Durham, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Geoffrey De Horderne est né environ 1176, à Durham, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, son père, R26 Richard HORDERNE, avait 26 ans et sa mère, ?, avait 23 ans. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec ?."},"de":{"ABT 1176–":"um 1176–Verstorben","1176–Male":"1176–Verstorben","1179–Female":"1179–Verstorben","–Male":"Verstorben","1152–Male":"1152–Verstorben","1155–Female":"1155–Verstorben","ABT 1176":"um 1176","1179":"1179","1155":"1155","1176":"1176","1152":"1152","HORDENE, DURHAM, ENGLAND":"Durham, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Als Geoffrey De Horderne um 1176 in Durham, England, Unit